snippet.title: Rumbleverse | Official Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
We are thrilled to be partnering with Iron Galaxy and proud to present Rumbleverse! Enter a 40-person melee to be crowned Champion in this Brawler-Royale.

Are you ready to touchdown in Grapital City?! Do you have what it takes to be Champion?!

Sign-up for Early Access here: http://www.rumbleverse.com/
